---
// DigitalStone.astro - Homepage Version
// Block 3: The Growth Engine
---

<section id="digital-stone" class="min-h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-8 snap-start relative border-t border-surface/30 section-pt">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full flex flex-col justify-center">
    
    <h2 class="text-xs md:text-sm font-body font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent mb-4 text-center md:text-left">
      The Path to Predictable ROI
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mt-4">
      
      <!-- Column 1: The Narrative -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight text-text-heading mb-6">
          An integrated growth engine, not just a scattered initiatives.
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Predictable growth doesn't come from just a marketing campaign or a better website. It comes from a unified system where your user acquisition strategy is directly connected to a technical foundation built to support it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          I architect this engine for you.
        </p>
        
        <div class="text-text-heading font-medium text-lg p-6 bg-surface/50 border-l-4 border-accent">
          <p>Stop paying for disconnected services. Start investing in a unified growth asset.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Spacer -->
      <div class="hidden md:block md:col-span-2"></div>

      <!-- Column 2: The Traits -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center bg-surface/20 p-8 md:p-10 border border-surface/50">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-text-heading mb-8 uppercase tracking-wide">
          What's a Growth Blueprint?
        </h3>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg list-none p-0 m-0">
          {[
            "A clear 180-day roadmap for 10x growth.",
            "A tech stack architecture for marketing and conversion.",
            "A data-driven user acquisition model.",
            "A guide to align Marketing channels with business goals.",
            "A system that provides clear ROI for your board.",
            "Full ownership of the entire growth infrastructure."
          ].map((item, index) => (
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class:list={["text-text-body", { "text-text-heading font-medium": index === 5 }]}>
                {item}
              </span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
